To run my evaluation code, please save the models, vectorizer, trainer, and generally all contents provided in the download links in the same directory as the notebook.

The challenge set is created by running the notebook, however, I will also submit it as a separate file. It can be inspected in the jupyter environment or treated as a json file with the following keys: 

	'capability'
        'test_type'
        'sent_str'
        'sent_tokens'
        'sent_predicate'
        'sent_gold'
        'sentence_number'  
        'checked_arg'
        'invariance'

A requirements.txt has been provided to you in the submission. 

After you have saved everything in the same directory as this notebook (datasets and contents of Google drive folders unzipped), you can safely run my code. 
